<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-1413] EstimatedHistogram.max is buggy</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-1413</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;EH.max returns the largest bucket floor, which will will be LESS than the largest value added to the histogram, which is not the usual behavior expected of a method called max.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12472062">CASSANDRA-1413</key>
            <summary>EstimatedHistogram.max is buggy</summary>
